import React from "react" const Location = (props) => { console.log(props) return (<>
  • {props.country}
  • {props.company}
  • {props.address}
  • {`${props.city}, ${props.state} ${props.zip} ${props.subCountry}`}
  • {`Tel.${props.tel}`}
  • {`Fax.${props.fax}`}
  • {`E-mail: ${props.email}`}
  • {`website: ${props.website}`}
) } export default Location
